{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Demonheart: The Cursed Trial is an otome visual novel set in a dark and mysterious world of demons and magic. Step into the shoes of a demonheart and fight for your survival in a twisted game of intrigue and betrayal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/headings_3_-_features.png?t=1727110342\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Female protagonist </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Hundreds of conversation choices - you pick nearly every line the main character says </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Two human male love interests (Ran and Kaisar); some flirting with a female human (Vita) and a male demonspawn </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> An alignment system for the main character </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Customizable name </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A dark story full of mystery and deceit </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Voice acting will be added when the full game is finished </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Bad guys and plot twists :) </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/circles_set1_620.png?t=1727110342\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/headings_3_-_plot.png?t=1727110342\" />You wake up in a strange place, only to realize you have been abducted along with seven other people. A city guard, a royal soldier, a witch, a bard, a librarian, and two criminals - all captured and brought together by an unknown force. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A demonspawn appears, delivering a chilling message: there are demonhearts among you - people blessed with regeneration, but cursed to be hunted by everyone else. You know the truth: you're one of them. And you'll do anything to keep your secret safe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As tensions rise and trust erodes, mysterious deaths start to occur. Can you trust anyone? Amidst the chaos, you may find yourself drawn to one of your fellow captives. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you survive the demonspawn's trial? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/circles_set2_620.png?t=1727110342\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This game is set in the <strong>Demonheart</strong> universe, but knowledge of the other Demonheart games is not needed to enjoy the story.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/headings_3_-_rel_620.png?t=1727110342\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chapters 1-6 - Released, word count: 133.000+</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chapter 7 (Final) - Planned release: Q1 2025 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Planned 160.000+ words for the whole game </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Voice acting will be added when all the chapters are finished</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Chapter 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2364560/6b58b01c195cf521b665c9737fb1e9bb3e9092dc.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2364560/991a0b7b3be9009ce8a10b16734de96d703489ab.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2364560/c1ccd503f1d90dc9632e7da1f5bd970be0b16807.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2364560/749d5db89e2a0f3397d7a94fd8acfc1218a84343.jpg"},{"name":"Chap